422
00:22:31,782 --> 00:22:34,082
Tapi, sayang sekali kurasa.

423
00:22:34,082 --> 00:22:37,282
Aku selalu berakhir seperti ini, bukan?

424
00:22:39,182 --> 00:22:41,482
Bahkan saat kasus ledakan bom

425
00:22:41,482 --> 00:22:43,682
dan kasus pria Hammer.

426
00:22:43,682 --> 00:22:44,882
Aku hampir berhasil,

427
00:22:44,882 --> 00:22:46,982
tapi sepertinya tidak bisa melewati.

428
00:22:52,082 --> 00:22:53,682
Dimana kamar Takagi?

429
00:22:53,682 --> 00:22:55,982
Aku rasa dia di kamar nomor 304.

